SUMMARY:D Talent Program Incentive Allocation Alignment Meeting
DTSTART;TZID=GMT 标准时间:20260416T160000
DTEND;TZID=GMT 标准时间:20260416T170000
CLASS:PUBLIC
DESCRIPTION:Dear all\,\n\n \n\n参见下附D Talent Program 2026年度上
 半年绩效分配方案。组个会完成项目管理机制。谢谢！\n
 \n \n\n会议议题：\n\n*  建立BCZ 数智化专项激励Policy。\n\n*
    政策目的\n\n*   适用范围\n\n*   激励对象\n\n*   激励类
 型\n\n*  项目落地奖励\n\n*  效益贡献奖励（核心）\n\n*  
 创新提案奖励\n\n*  专项奖金/荣誉激励\n\n*  年度优秀员
 工加分（已有）\n\n*  长期激励\n\n*   项目价值评估模型\n
 \n*   发放机制\n\n*   管理与评审机制\n\n*   约束与风险控
 制\n\n*   适用场景举例\n\n*  汇总上半年所有案例PPT（烦
 请各小组长协助准备）。\n\n*  最终绩效分配方案：\n\n\n\
 n \n\nBest Regards\,\n\nLily Liu\n\n \n\n_________________________________
 ____________\nFrom: Liu\, Xin06 \nSent: Friday\, April 10\, 2026 3:08 PM\n
 To: Sun\, Juan <juan.sun@benecke-changshun.com.cn>\; Xue\, Jialei <jialei.
 xue@benecke-changshun.com.cn>\; Shi\, Gino <gaofeng.shi@benecke-changshun.
 com.cn>\; Peng\, Lirong <lirong.peng@benecke-changshun.com.cn>\; Chen\, Ji
 ajun <jiajun.chen@benecke-changshun.com.cn>\; Tang\, Jiawei04 <jiawei.4.ta
 ng@benecke-changshun.com.cn>\; Li\, Xiaodong03 <xiaodong.3.li@benecke-chan
 gshun.com.cn>\nCc: Tian\, Richard <ming.tian@benecke-changshun.com.cn>\; Y
 ang\, Laraine <liping.yang@benecke-changshun.com.cn>\; Jia\, Xiaoge <xiaog
 e.jia@benecke-changshun.com.cn>\nSubject: RE: D Talent Program Incentive A
 llocation Alignment Meeting\n\n \n\nDear all\,\n\n \n\n参见下附会议
 纪要。如对奖励分配有任何异议或附加建议，请于2026/04/
 16（下周四）下班前以任何形式反馈给我。eSign签署计划
 在2026/04/17（下周五）开启。感谢！\n\n \n\n补充信息：\n\n
 *  新增“参与奖+”，为参加了现场展示但没能获奖的 D t
 alent 小组成员以资鼓励，受益人：吴晓娅（其他成员都
 有个人或团队奖励，特殊奖项不叠加）。\n\n*  “杰出贡
 献奖”将发放给确实落地的项目，本期轮空，在下半年
 的评选中，评选维度将新增“项目落地”。\n\n\n\n \n\n再
 次感谢大家对D Talent 项目的大力支持！❤\n\n \n\nBest regard
 s\,\n\n \n\nLily Liu(Liu Xin)\n\nME Engineer BCZ\n\nContiTech Surface Solu
 tions\n\n \n\nMobile: +86 189 5113 2980\n\nE-mail: xin.6.liu@benecke-chang
 shun.com.cn <mailto:xin.6.liu@benecke-changshun.com.cn> \n\nWebsite: www.c
 ontinental-industry.com <http://www.continental-industry.com/> \n\n \n\n--
 ---Original Appointment-----\nFrom: Liu\, Xin06 \nSent: Friday\, March 27\
 , 2026 3:39 PM\nTo: Liu\, Xin06\; Sun\, Juan\; Xue\, Jialei\; Shi\, Gino\;
  Peng\, Lirong\; Chen\, Jiajun\; Tang\, Jiawei04\; Li\, Xiaodong03\nCc: Ti
 an\, Richard\; Yang\, Laraine\; Jia\, Xiaoge\nSubject: D Talent Program In
 centive Allocation Alignment Meeting\nWhen: Friday\, April 10\, 2026 10:30
  AM-11:30 AM (UTC+08:00) Beijing\, Chongqing\, Hong Kong\, Urumqi.\nWhere:
  TE_ZG_MR_PlantOffice304_Zhangjiagang\n\n \n\nDear all\,\n\n \n\n感谢各
 位的大力支持，D Talent Program 2026 Q1季度交流会完美收官
 。约个会，现场讨论下项目激励如何分配。谢谢！\n\n \n\
 n下附为最终结果和补充信息，附件为评分细节表。\n\n \n
 \n\n\n \n\n\n\n \n\n\n\nBest Regards\,\n\nLily Liu\n\n \n\n_______________
 _________________________________________________________________\n\nMicro
 soft Teams meeting \n\nJoin: https://teams.microsoft.com/meet/353885945891
 59?p=NwppDc37vEzOr51LTP <https://teams.microsoft.com/meet/35388594589159?p
 =NwppDc37vEzOr51LTP>  \n\nMeeting ID: 353 885 945 891 59 \n\nPasscode: ni6
 2FW76 \n\n________________________________\n\nNeed help? <https://aka.ms/J
 oinTeamsMeeting?omkt=en-US>  | System reference <https://teams.microsoft.c
 om/l/meetup-join/19%3ameeting_NjE2MTQzZGItNTA4Ny00YzA4LWE0NjAtNTM5ZDRhNTQy
 Yjli%40thread.v2/0?context=%7b%22Tid%22%3a%228d4b558f-7b2e-40ba-ad1f-e04d7
 9e6265a%22%2c%22Oid%22%3a%221e3fea23-7c50-4fb2-a71b-c28eb213e712%22%7d>  \
 n\nFor organizers: Meeting options <https://teams.microsoft.com/meetingOpt
 ions/?organizerId=1e3fea23-7c50-4fb2-a71b-c28eb213e712&tenantId=8d4b558f-7
 b2e-40ba-ad1f-e04d79e6265a&threadId=19_meeting_NjE2MTQzZGItNTA4Ny00YzA4LWE
 0NjAtNTM5ZDRhNTQyYjli@thread.v2&messageId=0&language=en-US>  \n\nPrivacy a
 nd security <https://filehub.admiralcloud.com/dl/5/d6981e10-1775-44b3-92cf
 -aaf920ff7119>  \n\n______________________________________________________
 __________________________\n\n \n\n \n\n__________________________________
 ___________\nFrom: Liu\, Xin06 \nSent: Friday\, March 20\, 2026 8:42 AM\nT
 o: Jia\, Xiaoge <xiaoge.jia@benecke-changshun.com.cn <mailto:xiaoge.jia@be
 necke-changshun.com.cn> >\; Tian\, Richard <ming.tian@benecke-changshun.co
 m.cn <mailto:ming.tian@benecke-changshun.com.cn> >\; Yang\, Laraine <lipin
 g.yang@benecke-changshun.com.cn <mailto:liping.yang@benecke-changshun.com.
 cn> >\nCc: Sun\, Juan <juan.sun@benecke-changshun.com.cn <mailto:juan.sun@
 benecke-changshun.com.cn> >\; Xue\, Jialei <jialei.xue@benecke-changshun.c
 om.cn <mailto:jialei.xue@benecke-changshun.com.cn> >\nSubject: Budget Prop
 osal for the D Talent Program Award\n\n \n\nDear all\,\n\n \n\nFor informa
 tion only\; a formal e‑sign will follow shortly. Thank you!\n\n \n\nThis
  award recognizes teams and individuals who have demonstrated outstanding 
 performance in the D Talent Program. The final recipients will be determin
 ed through a group voting process on March 26\, 2026.\n\nWe request budget
  allocation to support this award\, covering the planned cash incentives f
 or the selected recipients. The awards will be paid together with payroll\
 , charged to Cost Center 43100 and Account K40702\, with taxes withheld co
 llectively.\n\n \n\nThis budget will enable us to:\n\n*  Recognize and rew
 ard outstanding contributions\n\n*  Encourage team engagement and high-qua
 lity project delivery\n\n*  Promote best practices and experience sharing 
 across the D Talent Program\n\n \n\nBest regards\,\n\n \n\nLily Liu(Liu Xi
 n)\n\nME Engineer BCZ\n\nContiTech Surface Solutions\n\n \n\nMobile: +86 1
 89 5113 2980\n\nE-mail: xin.6.liu@benecke-changshun.com.cn <mailto:xin.6.l
 iu@benecke-changshun.com.cn> \n\nWebsite: www.continental-industry.com <ht
 tp://www.continental-industry.com/> \n\n \n
