CLASS:PUBLIC
DESCRIPTION:Join us every other Monday at 14:30 CET for a 30-minute sessio
 n to explore Generative AI\, AI and Automation topics\, share insights\, a
 nd showcase exciting projects!\n💡 Want to present or suggest a topic?\n
 Reach out directly to @Rodrigues\, Catarina <mailto:catarina.cunha.rodrigu
 es@conti.de>  with your ideas!\nLet’s collaborate\, learn\, and innovate
  together. See you there!\n\nQuick Links\n\n*	\n	Everything you need to kn
 ow about the ContiGPT Community: ContiGPT Community (sharepoint.com) <http
 s://continental.sharepoint.com/teams/team_10065807/SitePages/ContiGPT-Comm
 unity.aspx> \n*	\n	Add these meetings to your calendar: Weekly Meeting - a
 dd it to your calendar <https://teams.microsoft.com/l/message/19:56fa358dd
 a644e9b90f35fbdedcbc080@thread.tacv2/1693830314815?tenantId=8d4b558f-7b2e-
 40ba-ad1f-e04d79e6265a&groupId=aa0b116e-6ae8-499b-94c2-a5bc76cb7243&parent
